    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"110049\">Mario Carneiro</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/287929-mathlib4/topic/Ordinal.2Esucc/near/526292516\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>and they aren't defeq</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Don't we have a typeclass for this? It's <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=SuccAddOrder#doc\">docs#SuccAddOrder</a></p>",
        "id": 526292553,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1751228214
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>oh is succ defined classically?</p>",
        "id": 526292558,
        "sender_full_name": "Kenny Lau",
        "timestamp": 1751228218
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>wait no succ is an explicit argument there</p>",
        "id": 526292580,
        "sender_full_name": "Kenny Lau",
        "timestamp": 1751228235
    },
    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">instance</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">SuccOrder</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ordinal</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">SuccOrder</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ofSuccLeIff</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">o</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">o</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">succ_le_iff'</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 526292622,
        "sender_full_name": "Kenny Lau",
        "timestamp": 1751228270
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Oh, so it is defeq?</p>",
        "id": 526292640,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1751228288
    },
    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">universe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">o</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ordinal</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">})</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Order</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">succ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">o</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">o</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rfl</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 526292649,
        "sender_full_name": "Kenny Lau",
        "timestamp": 1751228295
    },
